  "title": "Anticipatory differences between Attention and Expectation",
  "description": "This dataset investigates the neural mechanisms underlying anticipatory processing by comparing attention and expectation effects during a cognitive task. The study employs neuroimaging to dissociate how top-down attentional control and predictive expectation modulate brain activity in preparation for upcoming stimuli, providing insights into fundamental mechanisms of anticipatory cognition.",
